item.title: Project 1
item.description: Introduction I have combined 4 data sets for this project. The independent variables that are joined, common for all data sets, are year and country. The dependent variables I am assessing are country code, population, deaths due to terrorist attacks, banking crisis incidence, and number of vehicles produced in a year. I chose these data sets to analyze the correlation between all of these variables over time and in different countries.
